{   'html': '<article>         <div class="inCon">         <h1>武壇國際聯盟 World Wu Tan Kuoshu Federation (WWKF)</h1><span class="path"><a href="index.php">首頁</a> > <b>武壇國際聯盟</b></span>               <h2>緣起 Origin</h2><a name="organization-overview" id="organization-overview"></a>         <p>本聯盟為劉雲樵宗師門人所組國際平台，無會長、不分尊卑，唯以術會友、以道相連。<br>劉宗師所傳八極、八卦、螳螂，術德兼備，道寓於拳，薪火相傳。</p>         <h3>宗旨</h3>         <ol>             <li>傳承真脈</li>             <li>術德合一</li>             <li>四海同門</li>         </ol>         <p></p>         <p>A global, non-profit platform formed by disciples of Grandmaster Liu Yunqiao—without titles or ranks, united in martial spirit and shared path. <br>Grandmaster Liu’s Bajiquan, Baguazhang, and Tanglangquan emphasize both skill and virtue—his teachings live on through action and heart.</p>                 <h3>Mission</h3>         <ol>             <li>Preserve authentic lineage</li>             <li>Cultivate skill and virtue</li>             <li>Unite disciples worldwide</li>         </ol>         <p></p>                 <h2>Logo</h2><a name="wwkf-logo" id="wwkf-logo"></a>         <p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wutang.tw/images/WWKF-LOGO.png" class="wwkf-logo"></p>                          </div>         <div class="clear"></div>     </article>' } 